=== TEST 1: Prime cache for subsequent tests
--- http_config eval: $::HttpConfig
--- config
location /validation {
    content_by_lua '
        ledge:run()
    ';
}
location /__ledge_origin {
    content_by_lua '
        ngx.header["Cache-Control"] = "max-age=3600"
        ngx.header["Etag"] = "test1"
        ngx.header["Last-Modified"] = ngx.http_time(ngx.time() - 100)
        ngx.say("TEST 1")
    ';
}
--- request
GET /validation
--- response_body
